+Name: WinSparkle
+Short Name: winsparkle
+URL: https://github.com/vslavik/winsparkle
+Version: 0.9.2
+License: MIT
+License File: LICENSE
+Security Critical: yes
+Shipped: yes
+
+Description:
+WinSparkle is a software update framework for Windows, inspired by Sparkle for
+macOS. It provides automatic update checking, downloading, and installation
+functionality with built-in UI dialogs.
+
+Features used:
+- Automatic background update checking
+- EdDSA (ed25519) signature verification
+- Appcast XML feed parsing
+- Built-in update notification UI
+- Graceful shutdown callbacks for update installation
+
+Local Modifications:
+None. Using prebuilt binaries from official v0.9.2 release.
